v89 / v89.x ‚Äî The Continuum Bridge is built, sealed, and ready for copy-paste or upload.

Download the full repo (zip): codex-v89_repo.zip


Paste-into-GitHub (unzip or copy files as-is)

unzip codex-v89_repo.zip
cd codex-v89
git init
git branch -M main
git remote add origin https://github.com/<YOUR_USERNAME>/codex-v89.git
git add .
git commit -m "Codex v89.x ‚Äî The Continuum Bridge"
git tag -a v89.0 -m "v89 Bridge"
git tag -a v89.1 -m "v89.x Streams & Lightning stubs"
git push -u origin main --tags

Run locally

python -m venv .venv && source .venv/bin/activate
pip install -r requirements.txt
uvicorn src.knowledge.api:app --reload
# open http://127.0.0.1:8000/docs

API (new Bridge endpoints)

POST /bridge/sync ‚Üí initialize repo, create ATTST.v89.release.json, commit
body: {"remote":"https://github.com/<YOU>/codex-v89.git","signer":"cfbk-10-27-1998"}

POST /bridge/push ‚Üí push main to origin

POST /bridge/invoice ‚Üí Lightning invoice stub (msats)

POST /bridge/compose ‚Üí Compose via Neural Muse, create BTC payload hash, provisional receipt

POST /bridge/oracle ‚Üí Run a short async ‚Äúoracle stream‚Äù over glyphs


