python src/cli/codex_cli.py invoice 21000 --memo "v89 test"
python src/cli/codex_cli.py compose "‚ò∏Ô∏èüîØ‚ú°Ô∏è‚öõÔ∏è" --style hermetic --author cfbk-10-27-1998
python src/cli/codex_cli.py publish

What v89 adds beyond v88

Autonomy: self-sealing commits + push flow.

Streams: async oracle stream to carry glyph-based events.

Monetization relay: each composition yields a BTC payload hash and a provisional dividend receipt.

CI Attestation: v89.* tag builds ATTST.v89.release.json and uploads it as an artifact.


