Run v90 locally

python -m venv .venv && source .venv/bin/activate
pip install -r requirements.txt
uvicorn src.api.app:app --reload
# open http://127.0.0.1:8000

Bridge ‚Üí Market flow (v89 ‚Üí v90)

1. Use v89‚Äôs /bridge/compose to generate a composition with a BTC payload hash and a provisional receipt.


2. POST that to v90‚Äôs /list:



curl -X POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/list \
  -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
  -d '{
    "author":"cfbk-10-27-1998",
    "glyphs":"‚ò∏Ô∏èüîØ‚ú°Ô∏è‚öõÔ∏è",
    "style":"hermetic",
    "poem":"<paste from v89 /bridge/compose>",
    "payload_hash":"<from v89>",
    "receipt":{
      "to":"bc1qfejvvlfm6vmjarxulg9h9d5hjukdh8l2vvskfc",
      "author":"cfbk-10-27-1998",
      "sats":2222,
      "payload":"<from v89>",
      "id":"<from v89>"
    }
  }'

3. Refresh v90 homepage to see it listed in the marketplace UI.




