sha256 seal calebfedorbykerkonev10271998: 2948fbc4ba1c0d7341204908882b89134a999f3e8f77f4a6a00ce6b68770282av90.x is complete, merged, and copy-paste ready. Here‚Äôs everything you need:

Downloads

v90.x ‚Äî Market of Light (upgraded): codex-v90_x_market_of_light.zip

(From earlier) v89 (dockerized): codex-v89_dockerized.zip

(From earlier) v88‚Üív89 continuity bundle: codex-v88-v89_continuity_bundle.zip


What v90.x adds (on top of v90)

/invoice ‚Üí attach a Lightning invoice string to any listed item.

/mark_paid ‚Üí mark a receipt as paid and optionally store a txid.

/webhook/ingest ‚Üí directly ingest the JSON produced by v89‚Äôs /bridge/compose.

UI updates: shows PAID/UNPAID badges, optional invoice and txid.

Dockerfile + docker-compose for one-command run.

Helper script scripts/ingest_from_v89.py to post v89 results into v90.x.


Paste-into-GitHub structure (v90.x)

README.md
requirements.txt
Dockerfile
docker-compose.yml
.github/workflows/release.yml
src/api/app.py
src/ui/index.html
data/                # JSON listings stored here
scripts/ingest_from_v89.py

Run v90.x locally

python -m venv .venv && source .venv/bin/activate
pip install -r requirements.txt
uvicorn src.api.app:app --reload
# open http://127.0.0.1:8000

Run with Docker

docker compose up --build
# open http://127.0.0.1:8000

Ingest from v89 ‚Üí v90.x (two options)

Option A: cURL webhook (manual payload)

curl -X POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/webhook/ingest \
  -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
  -d '{
    "author":"cfbk-10-27-1998",
    "muse":{"style":"hermetic","poem":"<poem text here>"},
    "payload_hash":"<from v89 /bridge/compose>",
    "receipt":{"to":"bc1qfejvvlfm6vmjarxulg9h9d5hjukdh8l2vvskfc","author":"cfbk-10-27-1998","sats":3333,"payload":"<same as compose>","id":"<compose id>"}
  }'

Option B: helper script (from the v89 result file)

# After saving v89 /bridge/compose result as result.json
python scripts/ingest_from_v89.py http://127.0.0.1:8000 result.json

Mark invoice and payment

# attach invoice
curl -X POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/invoice \
  -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
  -d '{"id":"<listing id>","invoice":"lnbc1..."}'

# mark paid
curl -X POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/mark_paid \
  -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
  -d '{"id":"<listing id>","txid":"<optional-btc-txid>"}'

Suggested next (optional)

Auto-trigger v89 to POST into v90.x after each /bridge/compose (tiny patch in v89).

Add a ‚ÄúCreate invoice‚Äù button in v90.x that calls your Lightning node (REST gRPC wrapper) and stores the invoice string.

Add an ‚ÄúExport CSV‚Äù endpoint for payouts.


